{"nodes": [{"id": "docs_superpowers_specs_2026_07_06_grafico_evolucao_busca_design_grafico_evolucao_busca", "label": "Gr\u00e1fico de evolu\u00e7\u00e3o + respiro mobile + busca nos lan\u00e7amentos", "file_type": "document", "source_file": "docs/superpowers/specs/2026-07-06-grafico-evolucao-busca-design.md", "source_location": null, "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null, "rationale": "Tr\u00eas frentes: area chart substitui as barras mensais no detalhe da obra, respiro CSS no mobile (sem mudar cores/fontes \u2014 decis\u00e3o do pai), e busca textual nos lan\u00e7amentos. Regra do projeto: LER a skill dataviz antes de codar qualquer chart."}, {"id": "docs_superpowers_specs_2026_07_06_grafico_evolucao_busca_design_grafico_evolucao_da_obra", "label": "Gr\u00e1fico Evolu\u00e7\u00e3o da obra (bruto vs corrigido acumulados)", "file_type": "concept", "source_file": "docs/superpowers/specs/2026-07-06-grafico-evolucao-busca-design.md", "source_location": null, "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null, "rationale": "SVG puro gerado em app.js, sem lib (app \u00e9 PWA offline vanilla). Curvas Catmull-Rom \u2192 B\u00e9zier, gradiente sob a s\u00e9rie corrigida; a dist\u00e2ncia entre as duas linhas \u00e9 o juro embutido. Toque no m\u00eas destaca ponto e mostra valores acima do gr\u00e1fico \u2014 sem tooltip flutuante, mobile-first. M\u00e1x 24 pontos (janela mais recente)."}, {"id": "calc_serieevolucao", "label": "serieEvolucao(obra, taxaPct, hojeISO) (calc.js)", "file_type": "code", "source_file": "docs/superpowers/specs/2026-07-06-grafico-evolucao-busca-design.md", "source_location": null, "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null, "rationale": "Um ponto por m\u00eas-calend\u00e1rio entre o primeiro gasto e o fim da corre\u00e7\u00e3o; m\u00eas sem gasto repete o acumulado (bruto constante, corrigido continua rendendo); obra vendida congela no m\u00eas da venda."}, {"id": "docs_superpowers_specs_2026_07_06_grafico_evolucao_busca_design_busca_nos_lancamentos", "label": "Busca nos lan\u00e7amentos (texto + m\u00eas)", "file_type": "concept", "source_file": "docs/superpowers/specs/2026-07-06-grafico-evolucao-busca-design.md", "source_location": null, "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null, "rationale": "Casa descri\u00e7\u00e3o OU nome do t\u00f3pico, sem acento/mai\u00fascula (normalize('NFD') + strip diacr\u00edticos); busca textual sem sin\u00f4nimos. Filtros texto e m\u00eas combinam com E; contador achados/total. Filtro vive s\u00f3 em mem\u00f3ria \u2014 n\u00e3o salva na nuvem, some ao trocar de obra."}, {"id": "calc_filtragastos", "label": "filtraGastos(gastos, topicosMap, {texto, mes}) (calc.js)", "file_type": "code", "source_file": "docs/superpowers/specs/2026-07-06-grafico-evolucao-busca-design.md", "source_location": null, "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null}, {"id": "docs_superpowers_specs_2026_07_06_grafico_evolucao_busca_design_respiro_mobile", "label": "Respiro no mobile (s\u00f3 CSS)", "file_type": "concept", "source_file": "docs/superpowers/specs/2026-07-06-grafico-evolucao-busca-design.md", "source_location": null, "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null, "rationale": "Padding/gap maiores s\u00f3 em largura <768px, \u00e1rea de toque do li-del \u226540\u00d740px. Nada de mudar cores, fontes ou identidade \u2014 decis\u00e3o do pai."}], "edges": [{"source": "docs_superpowers_specs_2026_07_06_grafico_evolucao_busca_design_grafico_evolucao_busca", "target": "docs_superpowers_specs_2026_07_06_grafico_evolucao_busca_design_grafico_evolucao_da_obra", "relation": "references", "confidence": "EXTRACTED", "confidence_score": 1.0, "source_file": "docs/superpowers/specs/2026-07-06-grafico-evolucao-busca-design.md", "source_location": null, "weight": 1.0}, {"source": "docs_superpowers_specs_2026_07_06_gra